  <summary>4/15/1999--Introduced.
Small Business Regulatory Enforcement Fairness Implementation Act - Amends the Occupational Safety and Health Act of 1970 to provide for waiver of penalties for certain violations by small business concern employers, if such an employer corrects the violation within the time set for abatement.</summary>
